Class CallingMetricAccumulator

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GvcfMetricAccumulator

    public class CallingMetricAccumulator
extends java.lang.Object
implements VariantProcessor.Accumulator<CallingMetricAccumulator.Result>
    Collects variants and generates metrics about them. To use, construct, call setup(VCFHeader) once, then accumulate(htsjdk.variant.variantcontext.VariantContext) as desired, then call result().
